title: Master of All Skills
alternative_titles: Skill Collector: The Ultimate Skill Thief
summary: Master of All Skills Manhwa [Unique Trait ‘Skill Master (EX)’ has been activated.] ▶ ‘Skill Copy (EX)’ is now enabled. “Whoa… your skill’s insane!” [Skill has been copied.] From now on, there’s no skill he can’t have. Yours is mine. Mine? Still mine. With the power to copy any ability he witnesses, Yoo Ju-yeon embarks on a legendary journey to the top— outsmarting rivals, outshining heroes, and collecting every skill in existence. The rise of the ultimate cheat-class protagonist begins now. All Skill Master Yoo Ju-yeon’s explosive saga is just getting started! 올 스킬 마스터, Skill Collector: The Ultimate Skill Thief
